al relations in perilous times.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aAnimal welfarexMoral and ethical aspectszIraq. 0aCosmopolitanism. 0aHuman-animal relationshipsxPolitical aspects. 0aIraq War, 2003-2011xCasualties. 0aWar and society. 4aPhilosophy : Animal Rights. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 4aPolitics and Law : International Relations. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Science. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Violence in Society.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143848245340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438482453423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438482453/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles